bhavati tatra śalyaṃ vijānīyāt , sandhipranaṣṭe
          snehasvedopapannān sandhīn prasaraṇākuñcanabandhanapīḍanairbhṛśam upācaret;
          yatra saṃrambho vedanā vā bhavati

baddhvaikataś cāsya pañcāṅgyām upasaṃyatasyāśvasya vaktrakavike
